text:
Ariana Grande’s 6 albums if they were human siblings: 

Positions (2020):
~ AGE: 20
~RELATION: The oldest sister
~ PERSONALITY: The most responsible and mature sibling of them all who takes care of all her younger siblings and is the one in charge. Feeds them, disciplines them and takes charge all day every day. 
~ CLOSEST TO? All 5 of her younger siblings 

Thank U, Next (2019) 
~ AGE: 19
~RELATION: 2nd oldest sister 
~PERSONALITY: The most outgoing sibling who spends every late night out with her friends partying and drinking during the night. During the day, she’s the most introverted sibling who’s to herself and is always there for who ever needs advice regarding relationships. 
~ CLOSEST TO? Sweetener 

Sweetener (2018)
~AGE: 18
~RELATION: 3rd oldest sister 
~PERSONALITY : The most chill sibling of them all and tends to be the sweetest as well. She always obeys her older sisters and is very respectful towards her younger siblings as well. She spoils her younger siblings and spends as much as quality time with her older sisters. Whenever someone is sad, she’s always there to sing a sweet lullaby to cheer them up.
~CLOSEST TO? Positions 

Dangerous Woman (2016)
~AGE: 16
~RELATION: 4th oldest sister 
~PERSONALITY: The most rebellious of them all who thinks she can do whatever she wants just because she just turned 16. She never gets along with any of her siblings and always breaks the rules. She even sneaks out when no one is watching and meets up with boys who she knows from school and does some crazy stuff.
~CLOSEST TO? None 

My Everything (2014)
~AGE: 14
~RELATION: 5th oldest sister 
~PERSONALITY: The most conceited and sassy sibling who loves to pick on her younger sibling. She thinks she’s better than most of her siblings and acts like a princess. She doesn’t have time for no one’s crap and only gets along with boys she has a crush on. 
~CLOSEST TO? Yours Truly 

Yours Truly (2013)
~AGE: 13
~RELATION: The youngest sister
~PERSONALITY: the youngest sibling of them all who’s the most nicest and innocent sibling compared to all of her older sisters. She loves all her siblings equally and is The Sweet Angel that everyone loves (except for ‘My everything’). She never gets in trouble for anything and always listens to her oldest sister whenever she’s told to do something.
~ CLOSEST TO? My Everything
